{"tid":1865504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【LIVE】食衞局4點半就最新疫情情況及武肺「指定診所計劃」見記者","createTime":"2020-02-06T08:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T09:50:27.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"58bc1c18cc6950ea7ee0052ce8ebfb0a06e2e08a","tid":1865504,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:24:09.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局、衞生署及醫院管理局下午4時30分在中環統一碼頭道三十八號海港政府大樓二十五樓政府新聞處新聞會議室舉行簡報會，匯報新型冠狀病毒感染個案的最新情況，並簡介醫院管理局轄下指定診所的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局副局長徐德義、衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君、醫管局總行政經理（基層及社區醫療服務）夏敬恒和總行政經理（質素及標準）劉家獻將會出席。"},{"pid":"1d1db91fe99ae8964f9f775e3d14ff5980e9a86e","tid":1865504,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:24:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/live331a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flive331a&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAst%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=f1ea5971\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flive331a&h=0bd34ecf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/live331a</a>"},{"pid":"02493d4c8305cb5e73db2ee3f43bd846423f6499","tid":1865504,"uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"指定診所<br />\n唔知有幾多區會中獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf575c8911fa39a9027b104f318f5b3b092b3dbd","tid":1865504,"uid":192630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:28:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">運輸海關醫護罷工救港<br />\n各行各業立即大罷工</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"